{"tid":733822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日係新世紀超時空要塞 X 香港首播20週年】!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-07-08T06:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T08:57:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f6c75d8a8c08054d8708ac38736c28e47df81b8","tid":733822,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/141640_b06e27550b7a0d19d5de246b4702fdf6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F141640_b06e27550b7a0d19d5de246b4702fdf6.png&h=ecc987d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年無線受到對家亞視播放嘅「新世紀福音戰士」嘅熱潮影響，借意將Macross 7譯成「新世紀超時空要塞」<br />\n<br />\n故事講述麥克萊斯7號（NMCV-007）係人類嘅移民船團，在船團離開地球七年期間，突然受到神秘敵人「普羅多魔人」（Protodevilns）侵襲，船團被逼且戰且退。當軍方同敵人作戰期間，突然出現一位救星，一名搖滾樂手堅持在戰場唱歌，佢就係&ldquo;火焰巴沙拿&rdquo;，每當有敵人襲擊嘅時候，巴沙拿同佢嘅「火焰樂隊」全員都會唱歌畀敵人聽，但唔會開火 。無論敵方或者己方，都無人可以理解，不過最後都有人發現佢哋嘅歌聲充滿咗神奇力量，軍方更加特別授予「 歌樂戰隊」之稱號 。佢哋屢次驅逐敵人，在戰鬥中不斷磨煉。"},{"pid":"ad253b6d86897380b01ce2ea7b2cb95316298405","tid":733822,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c677561da0aa0cbc4a152996c1103594ca948dcf","tid":733822,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dce34072e39a3f2fe476e363269dd4f359ab80","tid":733822,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:46:16.000Z","msg":"當初睇係幾有趣<br />\n唱歌等於加BUFF又有FEEL<br />\n不過依家越做越爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9f07da60b2d9f7fe23910b2f0e696a94531032","tid":733822,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.g